notes:
### ROUND 1 – Setup Phase 🌀  
*Heal strong, poke sharp.*

**🟨 Core Power:**  
-  [Clone Conjuration](item_6c9f6be1-ab29-4f46-af24-34e4835f9af3)  – Your bread and butter. Opens up sustained healing early and sets the tone for your support role. Don’t skip it.

**🛍️ Starting Items:**  
-  [Compensator](item_2a354f80-610c-4661-9bdd-8960ae1a60b0)  – Smooths out shots for reliable headshot pressure.  
-  [Weapon Grease](item_961ae72f-434f-406b-a89b-ab8efec806bf)  – Faster handling = faster heals + better duels.  
-  [Armored Vest](item_358361e2-59be-4c81-b221-8a87f37809e6) * – Adds some early survivability while you’re scaling up.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- Prioritize **Weapon Power** from the jump — your healing and poke both scale with it.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- Focus on staying alive and keeping teammates topped off.  
- Take peeks for headshots when safe — early chip damage matters.  
- Play like a hybrid: heal when needed, poke when openings show.  
 *You’re setting up your flow — calm, precise, deadly.*

### ROUND 2 – Chakra Flow Deepens 🔮  
*Shift into full support mode if you're thriving.*

**🟨 Core Pickup:**  
-  [Teamwork Toolkit](item_d56fb90c-cbe6-4ad5-8475-0ce920f92a3f)  – If you're doing well and keeping up with the economy, grab this early. Adds a significant boost to your healing output and gives your team that extra edge in longer fights.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- Stick with **Weapon Power** to keep both your damage and healing scaling.  


**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- Now’s the time to lean harder into healing. Don’t tunnel vision damage — focus on value plays that keep your team in the fight.  
- Position to stay safe but relevant — *heal first, headshot second*.  
- Toolkit lets you clutch with faster, more effective support — capitalize on it.

### ROUND 3 – Mini Kitsune Mode 🦊  
*Utility spikes hard. Your heals now empower the squad.*

**🟨 Core Power:**  
-  [Supported Shooting](item_4a084906-0fcd-4158-9a4b-763a69d0b198)  – Adds a buff to allies you heal, giving them bonus damage for a short time. Pairs perfectly with  [Teamwork Toolkit](item_d56fb90c-cbe6-4ad5-8475-0ce920f92a3f)  — it’s basically a mini **Kitsune Rush** every time you throw support.

**🛠️ Item Upgrades:**  
-  [Talon Modification Module](item_c0ca1795-a3ea-4dc9-ae17-f34122574b3a)  – Big boost to weapon effectiveness. Helps with both damage and faster healing.  
- **(Optional)**:  [Compensator](item_2a354f80-610c-4661-9bdd-8960ae1a60b0)  and  [Weapon Grease](item_961ae72f-434f-406b-a89b-ab8efec806bf)  – Keep if you’ve got spare cash or if your aim needs a little tightening. Otherwise, focus on scaling core power.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- Still scaling with **Weapon Power** — that’s what fuels everything.  
- Look for **Cooldown Reduction** where possible to keep buffs and heals cycling fast.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- Position to tag multiple teammates with healing to spread that **Supported Shooting** buff.  
- Pre-heal brawlers before they go in — turns every engage into a bursty push.  
- You’re not just healing — you’re amplifying.

### ROUND 4 – Choose Your Path 🧭  
*Adapt to the match — empower or escape.*

**🟨 Power Options (Pick Based on Flow):**

-  [Spirits’ Guidance](item_25513335-271e-402b-bd03-9d082a281c40)  – If the game’s under control and you're staying safe, grab this for more **Weapon Power** and enhanced **healing output**. Keeps your scaling strong and your support sharp.

-  [Goddess’s Aura](item_a36d46c8-cee0-4c97-b6e4-72bb816c13dc)  – If you're getting **dove hard**, this is your lifeline. Sell  [Armored Vest](item_358361e2-59be-4c81-b221-8a87f37809e6) to replace this if you don't have enough.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- Keep investing in **Weapon Power** — the more you have, the more value you're delivering on every front.  
- Consider topping off **Cooldown Reduction** if fights are lasting longer or you're spamming abilities.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- With  [Spirits’ Guidance](item_25513335-271e-402b-bd03-9d082a281c40) , keep pressuring with heals and poke — you're nearing your full power curve.  
- With **Goddess Aura**, you can rely a lot more on your swiftstep.
- Either choice keeps you relevant — you're adapting, not falling behind.

### ROUND 5 – Healing in 4K 📡  
*Clones out, buffs stacked, heals non-stop.*

**🟨 Core Power:**  
-  [Leaf on the Wind](item_b64de259-d122-407d-a7e4-9d7267310704)  – Greatly boosts healing output while moving. Combined with  [Clone Conjuration](item_6c9f6be1-ab29-4f46-af24-34e4835f9af3) , this makes your healing feel omnipresent — you’re constantly repositioning and sustaining the whole squad.

**🛠️ Power Loadout Reminder:**  
- By now, you should have both  [Spirits’ Guidance](item_25513335-271e-402b-bd03-9d082a281c40)  and  [Goddess’s Aura](item_a36d46c8-cee0-4c97-b6e4-72bb816c13dc)  picked up, depending on your game flow.  
  - With both in your kit, you’ve got the best of both worlds: **enhanced healing output** and a **panic button teleport** that lets you survive dives and reposition when fights get messy.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- You should be nearing peak **Weapon Power**.  
- **Cooldown Reduction** should feel smooth — abilities up when you need them.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- Heal proactively — with  [Leaf on the Wind](item_b64de259-d122-407d-a7e4-9d7267310704)  and your clone, you can cover large zones with constant sustain.  
- Stay mobile — your movement is your healing.

### ROUND 6 – Tuning the Shrine 🔧  
*Now you're just optimizing greatness.*

**🛠️ Item Pickups:**  
-  [Icy Coolant](item_8b1c21e9-33e8-49a6-8277-a3a06d55a65f)  – Core pickup this round. Boosts both **Weapon Power** and **Cooldown Reduction**, letting you heal harder and more often.  
-  [Martian Mender](item_0099632b-4e18-450e-844f-22c40e51bc98)  *(Optional)* – If you're struggling to stay alive or getting focused, grab this for a mix of healing and survivability. Solid pick when fights get chaotic.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- If the match is going well, **double down on Weapon Power** with  [Icy Coolant](item_8b1c21e9-33e8-49a6-8277-a3a06d55a65f) . More damage, more healing — your entire kit benefits.  
- If you’re on the back foot or taking too much aggro, lean into **Martian Mender** instead to stay in the fight longer.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- By now, you're full support menace — dropping heals, teleporting, dashing, and dishing out clutch headshots.  
- Play based on team needs: *output more if you're ahead, stabilize more if you're behind*.  
- Don’t be afraid to reposition aggressively with Goddess Aura — you’ve got the tools to re-enter fights safely.

### ROUND 7 – The Finishing Touch 🍒  
*You're the last to die — if you die at all.*

**🟨 Final Power:**  
-  [Self-Care](item_0b7b0332-9bf6-4905-810e-7614b914d663)  – A simple but reliable pick to round out your loadout. Adds passive healing over time so you’re not reliant on teammates to keep you up. It’s the cherry on top — small, but clutch in long fights.

**🛠️ Final Item Call:**  
-  [Martian Mender](item_0099632b-4e18-450e-844f-22c40e51bc98)  – If not already locked in, this is the round to grab it. Boosts your survivability and helps you **stay upright during brawls**, especially when things get chaotic in overtime or final pushes.

**📈 Stat Focus:**  
- Weapon Power is likely capped or nearly there — now it’s all about **staying alive to keep your team alive**.  
- Any final scraps of **Cooldown Reduction** or **defense stats** are bonus.

**🎮 Playstyle Tips:**  
- You’ve got everything now: burst heals, clutch escapes, utility buffs, and now passive sustain.  
- Rotate smart, stay mobile, and **outlive everyone**.  
- Your team’s looking at you in the final fight — give ’em a reason to believe.
